{"tid":765224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡鞍鋼：中國已經超越美國  清華校友斥誤國誤民 聯署要求罷免教職","createTime":"2018-08-02T14:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T04:03:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e78e853725aaad30fe978ff68323afdf6383a998","tid":765224,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"【胡鞍鋼：中國已經超越美國】<br />\n【清華校友斥誤國誤民 聯署要求罷免教職】<br />\n<br />\n去年的一個清華大學高層論壇中，國情研究院院長胡鞍鋼直言：「中國的高技術產業已經超越美國。」此言一出，就馬上引起熱議，亦惹怒了一群清華校友。<br />\n<br />\n清華校友在網上發起聯署，要求解僱胡鞍鋼，在13個小時內已經收集近650個簽名。聯署書指，胡鞍鋼視學術為無物，誤導國家決策，又批評他的學術報告，以軍事人員加上軍事支出就等同於軍事資源，來評估中美的軍事力量，是貽笑大方，要求解除他清華大學國情研究院院長和教授職務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">胡鞍鋼自1985年起，已從事中國國情研究，他所撰寫的報告多次受到黨中央批示，甚至有「國師」之稱。自2015年開始，胡鞍鋼多次提出中國經濟總量已超越美國，又指中國的國際專利已超越日本，成為世界第二；到2020年之前，肯定會超越美國。</span><br />\n<br />\n面對民間的質疑，胡鞍鋼回應指，自己畢竟是專家，又指自己的研究是受到毛澤東的影響。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進，亦曾批評胡鞍鋼的主張違反常識，令他深感不安，但他周四在微博指，網民不斷人身攻擊的做法太「文革」。<br />\n<br />\n我們曾經嘗試兩次致電胡鞍鋼，但都聯繫不上。<br />\n<br />\n#胡鞍鋼<br />\n#中國已經超越美國<br />\n#清華大學<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"696f623451be52585b371b1ba50b5c7d48f12b58","tid":765224,"uid":49955,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"支持教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb0b2e989dcac785f4f62970f236ca48e08f283","tid":765224,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"胡鞍鋼真係極品黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64083d2263a0f697d1f5fea9cbfeeabe0e20620f","tid":765224,"uid":53687,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"呢650位人兄好快畀人思想改造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72727f14240d949e8fd243e51d94dc7c35b861f","tid":765224,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"到2020年之前，肯定會超越美國。<br />\n唔怪得俾人話誤國誤民 因為已經超越咗美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b845ebc78e73eae79a8201a792a5320715f7b74e","tid":765224,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T15:09:48.000Z","msg":"曲線滅支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ad1ec03272e9b2c4d1ae15d4b6c4ba5cc95b12","tid":765224,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb0b2e989dcac785f4f62970f236ca48e08f283","tid":765224,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"胡鞍鋼真係極品黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb75de9daae0c007a4ce99d07cc902c68eb1cc1","tid":765224,"uid":3508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:19:08.000Z","msg":"呢d人材支那一定要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3258abed43ede6ae7824d801222626d5f40b716","tid":765224,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:19:36.000Z","msg":"共匪一貫做法 搵人祭旗當自己無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f2bbd0ffe67bfe45105466ae3963bf0d5ddc2a","tid":765224,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:10:53.000Z","msg":"拍馬屁上位"},{"pid":"5d60d4b76d9ab27c1d604e1e56bdeb445e6dc70c","tid":765224,"uid":137506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"文革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超英趕美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鼓足幹勁 力爭上游 多快好省地建設社會主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e63f584840c531121038446dad7ff654dc2564","tid":765224,"uid"